{"tid":1522680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】火系魔法師要做足訓練，今日有手足懷疑嚴重燒傷","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:41:59.000Z","uid":33336,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13b82e7dcff593f515fd8e283f65255504a36839","tid":1522680,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我是和理非，核爆都唔割蓆<br />\n<br />\n我見到有個前線火系魔法師出魔法果陣，由於水馬太高，拋出魔法力度太細，布條塞得唔夠實 （唔知邊個原因啦）<br />\n<br />\n個魔法係水馬上面kick 一 kick，個魔法唔知跌左去邊一邊，然後手足就半邊身著左火<br />\n<br />\n佢身邊手足好快拍息左D火<br />\n<br />\n請各位法師吸夠經先上前線。<br />\n<br />\n希望手足無事"},{"pid":"cc9fd3be3c97c3d6de49fa80ef2edb5f8b3c3f73","tid":1522680,"uid":292497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"點樣吸夠經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好難架wor"},{"pid":"5583fe5b1ef24bf1c99f0d6cbfd3d94cf270535c","tid":1522680,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"各位手足要保重身體"},{"pid":"8b4e3448484b5e6331d99b2eef7217d9e2ac9a67","tid":1522680,"uid":33336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc9fd3be3c97c3d6de49fa80ef2edb5f8b3c3f73","tid":1522680,"uid":292497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"點樣吸夠經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好難架wor"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"用清水做防漏測試，手提滅火筒幫下身邊手足"},{"pid":"121c3d4ab6a7268fbb1698aefd97fc4317305463","tid":1522680,"uid":120715,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"火系魔法師係黑警黎"},{"pid":"da1855cc41a2f6fc3487b81eb36476197af1180d","tid":1522680,"uid":33336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5583fe5b1ef24bf1c99f0d6cbfd3d94cf270535c","tid":1522680,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"各位手足要保重身體"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"我唔知果位手足點，新聞無